to obstruct it also got contaminated with it.

35
00:03:57,813 --> 00:04:03,336
The only way one can really understand

36
00:04:04,106 --> 00:04:08,154
what we are is by knowing yourself.

37
00:04:08,709 --> 00:04:13,142
When you know yourself you are surprised that

38
00:04:13,770 --> 00:04:18,751
what is the greatest thing for you is to love and to be loved.

39
00:04:19,501 --> 00:04:23,399
 You enjoy that collective love so much

40
