00:21:46,317 --> 00:21:54,714
that on the birthday of Mother we will try to transform others.

123
00:21:54,739 --> 00:21:58,543
Our transformation has already been done but must do of others as well.

124
00:21:59,091 --> 00:22:04,783
This only  will give you complete contentment of this joy.

125
00:22:04,808 --> 00:22:07,408
Till now the joy you have is limited

126
00:22:07,433 --> 00:22:09,882
when you will distribute it among others

127
00:22:09,907 --> 00:22:12,611
and when it will be echoed in others

128
00:22:12,747 --> 00:22:19,893
when you will come to know about it, understand it

129
00:22:20,854 --> 00:22:28,469
a great new joy will awaken within yourself.

130
00:22:28,494 --> 00:22:37,737
I was watching your young boys, children dancing joyfully.

131
00:22:38,488 --> 00:22:43,912
Krishna got celebrated Holi so that everybody get joy.

132
00:22:43,937 --> 00:22:49,828
Shri Ram's style made a human being very serious type.

133
00:22:49,852 --> 00:22:52,293
His life became serious.

134
00:22:52,318 --> 00:22:55,468
He (Shri Krishna) devised a method so that a human being

135
00:22:55,493 --> 00:22:58,477
 cound open up himself and play mirthfully.

136
00:22:58,802 --> 00:23:02,865
Now that thing only Sahajyogis can do practically

137
00:23:02,890 --> 00:23:07,702
can play Holi with love amongst themselves.

138
00:23:07,727 --> 00:23:11,146
Not to trouble others

139
00:23:11,171 --> 00:23:17,561
but to express their own joy and to make feel others joyous as well.

140
00:23:18,538 --> 00:23:20,759
Eternal blessings to everyone.

 